L. Akli, M. Madrid, J. Alameda, L. Rivers, S. Gordon, “XSEDE Training: Achieving Access and Inclusion”, Proceeding of the XSEDE16 Conference on Diversity, Big Data, and Science at Scale, 2016, DOI: [10.1145/2949550.2949586](http://dx.doi.org/10.1145/2949550.2949586).

